unt of data.</li>\r\n 	<li>Knowledge of databases, web analytics, CRM systems and SEO.</li>\r\n 	<li>Strong communication and presentation skills.</li>\r\n 	<li>Knowledge of data warehousing, modeling, and mining.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Good to have</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Experience with Hadoop &amp; big data.</li>\r\n 	<li>Knowledge with cloud computing, SaaS, Paas and IaaS.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Company Benefit Plan includes</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>New hire and ongoing training and development.</li>\r\n 	<li>Established territory with market leading products.</li>\r\n 	<li>Medical Insurance.</li>\r\n 	<li>Health Savings Account.</li>\r\n 	<li>Supplemental Insurance.</li>\r\n 	<li>Employer paid Life Insurance.</li>\r\n 	<li>30+ Paid leaves annually.</li>\r\n</ul>";s:10:"post_title";s:17:"Marketing Analyst";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:6:"closed";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:17:"marketing-analyst";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2017-07-09 11:11:02";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2017-07-09 11:11:02";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:0;s:4:"guid";s:54:"http://localhost/wp/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=1120";s:10:"menu_order";i:0;s:9:"post_type";s:11:"job_listing";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:6:"filter";s:3:"raw";}i:2;O:7:"WP_Post":24:{s:2:"ID";i:1119;s:11:"post_author";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2017-07-09 10:30:23";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2017-07-09 10:30:23";s:12:"post_content";s:1630:"Just as the name suggests, we are currently looking for tech support. Grab on to this as this is one of our work from home opportunities you can find (freshers can apply).\r\n<h3>Requirements</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Strong work ethic, detail oriented as well as excellent oral and written communication skills <strong>is mandatory</strong>.</li>\r\n 	<li>Knowledge of multiple desktop programs, configuration and debugging techniques.</li>\r\n 	<li>Should have knowledge in windows , installation, troubleshooting, router configuration.</li>\r\n 	<li>Must have good knowledge in Desktop &amp; Networks basic.</li>\r\n 	<li>Knowledge of git and Linux environment is a plus.</li>\r\n 	<li>Sound problem resolution, judgment and decision-making</li>\r\n 	<li>Troubleshooting Windows Installation Technical Support Problem Resolution Router Configuration Communication Skills</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Good to have</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>UG: B.Com - Commerce, B.A - Any Specialization, BCA - Computers, B.Sc - Any Specialization, Computers, Electronics, Maths, B.Tech/B.E. - Any Specialization, Computers, Electronics/Telecommunication</li>\r\n 	<li>PG: MCA - Computers, MS/M.Sc(Science) - Any Specialization, Computers, Electronics &amp; Embedded Technology, Electronics, M.Com - Commerce.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Company Benefit Plan includes:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>New hire and ongoing training and development.</li>\r\n 	<li>Established territory with market leading products.</li>\r\n 	<li>Medical Insurance.</li>\r\n 	<li>Health Savings Account.</li>\r\n 	<li>Supplemental Insurance.</li>\r\n 	<li>Employer paid Life Insurance.</li>\r\n 	<li>30+ Paid leaves annually.</li>\r\n</ul>";s:10:"post_title";s:12:"Tech Support";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:6:"closed";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:12:"tech-support";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2017-07-09 10:30:23";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2017-07-09 10:30:23";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:0;s:4:"guid";s:54:"http://localhost/wp/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=1119";s:10:"menu_order";i:0;s:9:"post_type";s:11:"job_listing";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:6:"filter";s:3:"raw";}i:3;O:7:"WP_Post":24:{s:2:"ID";i:1117;s:11:"post_author";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2017-07-09 10:18:20";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2017-07-09 10:18:20";s:12:"post_content";s:1913:"GMR is seeking an inside sales professional who loves the challenge of selling into high level executives and is comfortable hunting and closing deals. Challenge yourself and get ready to prove that you have what it takes to be a top producer. This is the best opportunity you can grab as you will be working from home with flexible timings (client &amp; zone specific).\r\n<h3>Responsibilities</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Responsible for meeting a sales quota in the Municipal, Cooperative, and International Utilities markets.</li>\r\n 	<li>Manage a territory and prospect business on a daily basis via telephone and email.</li>\r\n 	<li>Conducts telephone and web based presentations to close business and increase customer utilization of GMR products.</li>\r\n 	<li>Consistently meet or exceed metrics of 50 calls per day.</li>\r\n 	<li>Conduct occasional face to face sales presentations and attended trade shows to close larger opportunities</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Requirements</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Bachelors degree in business, marketing or equivalent.</li>\r\n 	<li>3-4 years of face-to-face or inside sales, B2B or Business Development experience.</li>\r\n 	<li>Highly self-motivated and self-disciplined.</li>\r\n 	<li>Outgoing personality with expertise at developing relationships, particularly with operations managers, engineers and technicians.</li>\r\n 	<li>Good communicatorexcellent listening skills and ability to undercover the real problems that a client might be experiencing</li>\r\n 	<li>Ability to begin work immediately</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Company Benefit Plan includes</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>New hire and ongoing training and development.</li>\r\n 	<li>Established territory with market leading products.</li>\r\n 	<li>Work from home.</li>\r\n 	<li>Medical Insurance.</li>\r\n 	<li>Health Savings Account.</li>\r\n 	<li>Supplemental Insurance.</li>\r\n 	<li>Employer paid Life Insurance.</li>\r\n 	<li>30+ Paid leaves annually.</li>\r\n</ul>";s:10:"post_title";s:15:"Sales executive";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:6:"closed";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:15:"sales-executive";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2017-07-09 10:32:51";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2017-07-09 10:32:51";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:0;s:4:"guid";s:54:"http://localhost/wp/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=1117";s:10:"menu_order";i:0;s:9:"post_type";s:11:"job_listing";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:6:"filter";s:3:"raw";}i:4;O:7:"WP_Post":24:{s:2:"ID";i:1115;s:11:"post_author";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2017-07-08 22:38:27";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2017-07-08 22:38:27";s:12:"post_content";s:2554:"Were looking for an experienced Senior Web Developer to work directly with our product team using your skill in browser technologies including HTML/CSS, Javascript &amp; php.\r\n<h3>Responsibilities</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Work independently and within a team to maintain (team size - 4) and develop websites.</li>\r\n 	<li>Mentor and assist other developers with skill development, techniques, standards and troubleshooting.</li>\r\n 	<li>Develop and ensure standards across all web technologies within the web content management domain.</li>\r\n 	<li>Documentation of the tasks and the architecture changes related to web development.</li>\r\n 	<li>Assist troubleshooting efforts for complex problems.</li>\r\n 	<li>Code and test third party integrations, and work collaboratively with others to execute the plan most effectively.</li>\r\n 	<li>Create, document and maintain technical designs.</li>\r\n 	<li>Maintain reports for accountability and productivity measures. Aid in providing ongoing analysis and monitoring.</li>\r\n 	<li>Provide accurate estimates of development tasks for self and others.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Requirements</h3>\r\nYou will be required to design, develop, and implement rich user interface for our web based system. Gathering and analysis of the business requirements and converting them to technical specifications. Peer code reviews, unit testing, and continuous integration can be considered as a part of daily activity. Flexible to work with diverse development platforms, software, hardware, technologies and tools.\r\n<h3>Good to have</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Github sample of your work (if available).</li>\r\n 	<li>At least one version control system knowledge.</li>\r\n 	<li>Advanced knowledge of Javascript, HTML4/5, CSS2/3, JQuery, Bootstrap, Angular, XML/JSON, PHP.</li>\r\n 	<li>Front-end development experience using client side MVC in a large scale web operation.</li>\r\n 	<li>Building Responsive and/or Adaptive UI.</li>\r\n 	<li>Expert User Experience and usability knowledge.</li>\r\n 	<li>Advance knowledge of web standards, accessibility and usability.</li>\r\n 	<li>Must be a team player.</li>\r\n 	<li>Performs other duties as required or requested.</li>\r\n 	<li>Contributes to the positive team efforts of the office, the department, and the company.</li>\r\n 	<li>Knowledgable about Scrum and its working techniques.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Company Benefit Plan</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Medical Insurance</li>\r\n 	<li>Health Savings Account</li>\r\n 	<li>Supplemental Insurance</li>\r\n 	<li>Employer paid Life Insurance</li>\r\n 	<li>30+ Paid leaves annually.</li>\r\n</ul>";s:10:"post_title";s:20:"Senior Web Developer";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:6:"closed";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:20:"senior-web-developer";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2017-07-09 10:31:27";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2017-07-09 10:31:27";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:0;s:4:"guid";s:54:"http: