(1115, 0, '2017-07-08 22:38:27', '2017-07-08 22:38:27', 'Were looking for an experienced Senior Web Developer to work directly with our product team using your skill in browser technologies including HTML/CSS, Javascript &amp; php.\r\n<h3>Responsibilities</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Work independently and within a team to maintain (team size - 4) and develop websites.</li>\r\n 	<li>Mentor and assist other developers with skill development, techniques, standards and troubleshooting.</li>\r\n 	<li>Develop and ensure standards across all web technologies within the web content management domain.</li>\r\n 	<li>Documentation of the tasks and the architecture changes related to web development.</li>\r\n 	<li>Assist troubleshooting efforts for complex problems.</li>\r\n 	<li>Code and test third party integrations, and work collaboratively with others to execute the plan most effectively.</li>\r\n 	<li>Create, document and maintain technical designs.</li>\r\n 	<li>Maintain reports for accountability and productivity measures. Aid in providing ongoing analysis and monitoring.</li>\r\n 	<li>Provide accurate estimates of development tasks for self and others.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Requirements</h3>\r\nYou will be required to design, develop, and implement rich user interface for our web based system. Gathering and analysis of the business requirements and converting them to technical specifications. Peer code reviews, unit testing, and continuous integration can be considered as a part of daily activity. Flexible to work with diverse development platforms, software, hardware, technologies and tools.\r\n<h3>Good to have</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Github sample of your work (if available).</li>\r\n 	<li>At least one version control system knowledge.</li>\r\n 	<li>Advanced knowledge of Javascript, HTML4/5, CSS2/3, JQuery, Bootstrap, Angular, XML/JSON, PHP.</li>\r\n 	<li>Front-end development experience using client side MVC in a large scale web operation.</li>\r\n 	<li>Building Responsive and/or Adaptive UI.</li>\r\n 	<li>Expert User Experience and usability knowledge.</li>\r\n 	<li>Advance knowledge of web standards, accessibility and usability.</li>\r\n 	<li>Must be a team player.</li>\r\n 	<li>Performs other duties as required or requested.</li>\r\n 	<li>Contributes to the positive team efforts of the office, the department, and the company.</li>\r\n 	<li>Knowledgable about Scrum and its working techniques.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Company Benefit Plan</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Medical Insurance</li>\r\n 	<li>Health Savings Account</li>\r\n 	<li>Supplemental Insurance</li>\r\n 	<li>Employer paid Life Insurance</li>\r\n 	<li>30+ Paid leaves annually.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Senior Web Developer', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'senior-web-developer', '', '', '2017-07-09 10:31:27', '2017-07-09 10:31:27', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wp/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=1115', 0, 'job_listing', '', 0),
